Package: insetplot
Title: Inset Plots for Spatial Data Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chao", "Kong", , "kongchao1998@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6404-6142"))
Description: Create inset plots for spatial data visualization with minimal modifications to existing 'ggplot2' code. You provide the extent and size of the inset, simply wrap your existing plotting code and it will handle the rest: data cropping, aspect ratio handling, and layout management.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
